hcare, transportation or retail, companies across all \\nindustries are excited about investing in building intelligent \\nsolutions. Meanwhile, let\\u2019s hope human intelligence remains \\nuncontested&nbsp;:).<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><h3 name=\\"696e\\" id=\\"696e\\" class=\\"graf graf--h3 graf-after--p\\">Trending AI Articles:<\\/h3><p><br><\\/p><blockquote name=\\"9232\\" id=\\"9232\\" class=\\"graf graf--pullquote graf-after--h3\\"><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/chatbotslife.com\\/how-neural-networks-work-ff4c7ad371f7\\" data-href=\\"https:\\/\\/chatbotslife.com\\/how-neural-networks-work-ff4c7ad371f7\\" class=\\"markup--anchor markup--pullquote-anchor\\" rel=\\"noopener\\" target=\\"_blank\\">1. How Neural Networks&nbsp;Work<\\/a><\\/blockquote><p><br><\\/p><blockquote name=\\"8eee\\" id=\\"8eee\\" class=\\"graf graf--pullquote graf-after--pullquote\\"><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/chatbotslife.com\\/resnets-highwaynets-and-densenets-oh-my-9bb15918ee32\\" data-href=\\"https:\\/\\/chatbotslife.com\\/resnets-highwaynets-and-densenets-oh-my-9bb15918ee32\\" class=\\"markup--anchor markup--pullquote-anchor\\" rel=\\"noopener\\" target=\\"_blank\\">2. ResNets, HighwayNets, and DenseNets, Oh&nbsp;My!<\\/a><\\/blockquote><p><br><\\/p><blockquote name=\\"2c6a\\" id=\\"2c6a\\" class=\\"graf graf--pullquote graf-after--pullquote\\"><a href=\\"https:\\/\\/chatbotslife.com\\/machine-learning-for-dummies-part-1-dbaca076ec07\\" data-href=\\"https:\\/\\/chatbotslife.com\\/machine-learning-for-dummies-part-1-dbaca076ec07\\" class=\\"markup--anchor markup--pullquote-anchor\\" rel=\\"noopener\\" target=\\"_blank\\">3. Machine Learning for&nbsp;Dummies<\\/a><\\/blockquote><p><br><\\/p><p name=\\"03f2\\" id=\\"03f2\\" class=\\"graf graf--p graf-after--pullquote\\">In\\n the actual case, a solution such as a powerful image classifier can \\nhelp the company track shelf inventory, categorize products, record \\nproduct volume, etc. from raw products images captured in real time by \\ndedicated devices 