, Maharashtra, Tamil Nadu, Gujarat, Assam, Chhattisgarh, Kerala, Meghalaya, Orissa, Tripura and Madhya Pradesh. In case of salaried employees and wage earners, Employer is liable to deduct professional tax with the State Government. In case of other class of Individuals, this tax is liable to be paid by the person himself. IndiaFilings can help obtain professional tax registration in India, from just Rs.12899.<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/section>","description":"Tax Registration","header":"","footer":"","keywords":"","eq_check":"0","status":"1","timestamp":"2018-07-31 17:02:18"}]', '2018-08-20 10:27:38'),
