(117, 'Industry', '4', 124, 0, 0, 0, '', 0, '<img src="http://www.softlabsgroup.com/Software_Companies_Mumbai_India_images/Web_Cloud_Solutions.jpg" alt="image" style="height:400px;" width="100%">\n<h2 style="text-align: center; "><span style="font-size: 24px;">INDUSTRIES</span></h2> \n<p style="margin-left: 25px;style=" text-align:justify;"=""><span style="font-size: 14px;"><font color="#424242">Flex provides BPO services which deliver an all-encompassing solution for businesses in a vast array of industries. We have developed a thorough understanding of the challenges that businesses within these industries face and provide solutions to allow our clients to overcome these challenges and achieve differentiation in their market. Flex streamlines processes for the following industries.We are delighted with the high level of accuracy that Flex demonstrates in the data indexing and signed health verification processes. Outsourcing has given us the time to focus on our patients, business and services, and we are very satisfied with our decision of choosing Flex as a partner."We are delighted with the high level of accuracy that Flex demonstrates in the data indexing and signed health verification processes. Outsourcing has given us the time to focus on our patients, business and services, and we are very satisfied with our decision of choosing Flex as a partner."</font></span></p>\n<p style="margin-left: 25px;">\n<span style="font-size: 14px;"><font color="#424242">Value-added Consultation\nHaving considerable experience and expertise in delivering global BPO services, we ensure that our value added consultations provides the right answers to your business challenge.\n\nEnd to End Services\nEnd to End Customized Services Flex provides end-to-end customized business process optimization services across major business functions and industry verticals ensuring on-time fulfilment of tasks.\n\nCollaborative development\nScalable and On-Time Delivery Flex possesses deep seated capabilities to scale up services in accordance with changing requirements, ensuring the continuity and on-time completion of your project.\n\nAccelerated delivery\nBusiness Continuity Planning\nWe have extensive industry knowledge, resources, skilled personnel, systems, plans and processes in place that ensure business continuity in case of an emergency situation.\n\n\nComplete transparency\nQuality and Compliance\nWe have achieved compliance . We adhere to impeccable quality standards as per ISO 9001:2008, in all processes, leading to high quality output.</font></span>\n</p>', 'industry desc', '', '', '', 0, 1, '2018-09-06 09:57:33'),
(118, 'Resources', '4', 125, 0, 0, 0, '', 0, '<img src="https://www.invensis.net/slider-image/header-banner-dark.png" alt="image" height="60%" width="110%">\n\n<p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><b><font color="#424242">Resources</font></b></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><font color="#424242">U.K. based strategic marketing intelligence and data solution expert mandated Flex Technologies with the requirement of manual data entry and processing of four types of scanned handwritten forms collected from different customers. Download the case study to find out how Flex'' team of experienced and qualified data entry professionals helped the client in processing 50,000+ forms per month with 99% accuracy.\nAn international hospitality chain, with a geographical footprint of over, mandated Flex Technologies to manage their customer correspondence that numbered in the thousands per day. Download the case study to find out how Flex delivered positive outcomes to the client that facilitated their customer relationship management initiatives.\n</font></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><font color="#424242">Innovative software application development company approached Flex&nbsp;with the requirement of carrying out extensive market research using tele calling to identify suitable child-friendly restaurants and eateries in the UK and US to be used for their app database. Download the case study to find out how Flex'' market research call center services enabled the client to update their database and boost app development.\nAn international supplier of luxury car parts and accessories turned to Flex Technologies to provide an inbound call center with the capability of handling large volumes of customer communication. Download the case study to find out how Flex delivered the benefits of outsourcing to the client and enabled them to focus on their core capability.</font></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><font color="#424242"><br></font></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span><br></p>\n', 'resources desc', '', '', '', 0, 1, '2018-09-06 08:11:34');
